{"tid":271544,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"由幾時開始短片變左叫微電影？","createTime":"2017-06-05T07:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T13:41:20.000Z","uid":4880,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"56074a758d3bbb2508964a7d665bbed457338c75","tid":271544,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T07:30:07.000Z","msg":"同埋咩叫屌打？屌完再打？"},{"pid":"37d6ec2d7aebe845c1befcbc6ab33d0a4af6e1d4","tid":271544,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T07:38:00.000Z","msg":"冇膽匪類，棚尾拉箱。。係咪要講番呢D舊野？"},{"pid":"f0367e561a883f037f3e02197ef24f7cb0f1d3ad","tid":271544,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T09:38:07.000Z","msg":"我仲以為凡係放得係youtube嘅video就可以叫短片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc63910aa8964669b59e8656b74e08213c2b7b7","tid":271544,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T09:48:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇膽匪類，棚尾拉箱。。係咪要講番呢D舊野？</blockquote><br />\n點解呢啲又無人話要守護嘅？<br />\n而一講到咩屈機吊打就個個發晒癲咁"},{"pid":"54809dfcc3d2631a7aaef36695f722b5f6e7cbc2","tid":271544,"uid":52816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T10:47:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e8d50aef3df212e5df1146fb5ec141625fcd969","tid":271544,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T10:49:36.000Z","msg":"召喚書面語達人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51c59f3ba97d147dfd87b3da37e471c6f2286b9f","tid":271544,"uid":113929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T11:12:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇膽匪類，棚尾拉箱。。係咪要講番呢D舊野？</blockquote><br />\n唔係舊唔舊問題，係成個詞語語不達意"},{"pid":"efb6a98e6282d97893ba128f364cc31f9f30ef8d","tid":271544,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T13:38:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇膽匪類，棚尾拉箱。。係咪要講番呢D舊野？</blockquote><br />\n唔係舊唔舊問題，係成個詞語語不達意</blockquote><br />\n傳達意思不嬲都係精簡"},{"pid":"ccb41b0ff1be958c329372641b2eecc4199ce19c","tid":271544,"uid":4880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T13:39:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>短片同微電影唔同。<br />\n微電影定義上應該都係短片嘅一種嘅。<br />\n<br />\n不過我覺得「電影」一詞，用作描述「一部電影」其實已經唔係太準確。<br />\n<br />\n電影係一種播放方式，我估係將底片用光投射落布幕，因為類似皮影戲果類嘢所以先叫電影。<br />\n<br />\n就好似你唔會叫一套劇或者一個節目做電視。<br />\n<br />\n所以我地唔應該將作品稱呼為「電影」，應該將佢地稱呼做「戲」。<br />\n<br />\n所以「微電影」應該改做「微戲」<br />\n講笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔計上面講嘅嘢，「微電影」一詞令人覺得難聽嘅原因應該係造詞嘅韻律、節奏或者結構同香港人平時講開嘅唔太夾。<br />\n<br />\n唔係乜嘢字都可以直接加埋，例如微蜜蜂、微雪糕。<br />\n<br />\n而且微電影真係好有直譯feel，好似將micrometer譯做微米咁譯。</blockquote><br />\n咪即係短片囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01cb789ab54932e2e273d8e448bcd10fe2f50512","tid":271544,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T13:41:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我仲以為凡係放得係youtube嘅video就可以叫短片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁有好多subgenre je,只係短片同微電影呢兩個terms overlap左，咁點解叫開短片忽然變左微電影？"}]}